00:00:16.690 --> 00:00:18.859
(Kim Ju Hun)

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.789
(Kim Min Kyu)

00:00:39.909 --> 00:00:43.879
(Missing Crown Prince)

00:00:43.880 --> 00:00:45.218
(All characters, locations, organizations, and incidents...)

00:00:45.219 --> 00:00:46.478
